        <Summary>A saturation equalizer plugin for GIMP</Summary>
        <Description>Saturation equalizer lets you modify saturation of an image more precisely, f.e. enhance saturation of less saturated areas, but avoid oversaturation of more saturated pixels. In addition, you can modify brightness similarly as levels tool work. Plugin also enables to change a temperature of image.</Description>
